# Gas Detector Project

This is a simple *Arduino Gas Detection System* using the MQ sensor, LED, and buzzer.

## Components Used
- Arduino UNO
- MQ-2 / MQ-6 Gas Sensor
- LED
- Buzzer
- Jumper Wires
- Breadboard

## Features
✔ Detects gas leakage  
✔ Alerts using LED and buzzer  
✔ Displays concentration values in serial monitor

